{"hash":"eadc1cf98272e6635158b52ac6167ef00a990c8e","data":{"markdownPage":{"id":"15b7be32a528a56e54395200d605c60b","title":"이벤트스토밍","description":"","path":"/business/","timeToRead":2,"content":"<h1 id=\"이벤트스토밍\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4%EB%B2%A4%ED%8A%B8%EC%8A%A4%ED%86%A0%EB%B0%8D\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>이벤트스토밍</h1>\n<p>쇼핑몰 시나리오를 기반으로 이벤트스토밍을 수행합니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"msaez-모델링-도구-접속\"><a href=\"#msaez-%EB%AA%A8%EB%8D%B8%EB%A7%81-%EB%8F%84%EA%B5%AC-%EC%A0%91%EC%86%8D\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>MSAEZ 모델링 도구 접속</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>크롬 브라우저를 실행하고 <a href=\"https://www.msaez.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.msaez.io</a> 에 접속합니다.</li>\n<li>우측 상단의 아바타 아이콘을 클릭하여 <strong>깃헙(Github)</strong> 계정으로 로그인 합니다.</li>\n<li><strong>만들기</strong> > <strong>이벤트스토밍</strong> 을 클릭합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1919 963' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-ce83f23b7856602a3cf1363a241a26f5'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-ce83f23b7856602a3cf1363a241a26f5)' width='1919' height='963' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAgCAYAAACinX6EAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAGwUlEQVRo3uVZ6W9UVRSvJv4Pmpi4xU8CouELiOAGxgRUNlFQPohIWglgBEU0IoJlqbJYwA3KIlsQMYgJ0IJQWhtDoEALdO/Qdqazb%2b/N3jf35zm382ZeVzrTaWvinZzce9%2b97757fme790xO1N0sTv6yTRTuPifqqxoFAKFpcZFpCYfDkjo6OkQ8HhehUEhEIhHZjsVicoxr7nM7Ek2N8VxN0%2bS7TFzi4i57iXfOAFHr9evCVlcnwjabUMxmYaU6EAgIG9UtLS1CDQZFxOcVsRazCJmsItpuETmIBUVl2V4cO3MMfk8AXHi9TIvP54PX60U0GgUxBrfbDUVR5JrEIDwej6x5jOfxGLeDwSBcLpd8j5gHAZLcC48z9bUv0TkRTeXlqLt8GWpzM%2bw1Naitr4dK67e1taGB2g5aP%2bLywGYxobjyNGJ2G3L09xO1BFWvMyn6Otkg1oLuz1hDWGOMezTuW1J/%2b6Bfh%2bIVIbdFRFVV5CT0CKm1OlFPRwuM8/V2psTFKG2uGxoaUF